00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,600
If you can't reach me today,

292
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:41,640
and we don't meet each other,

293
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,640
where do you live?

294
00:18:42,760 --> 00:18:43,420
This time,

295
00:18:43,560 --> 00:18:44,260
your mum and I

296
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:45,990
are here for the class reunion.

297
00:18:46,090 --> 00:18:48,020
Of course we're staying in a hotel.

298
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:49,480
She's here too.

299
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:51,800
Where is she?

300
00:18:52,140 --> 00:18:53,070
You know

301
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:55,000
your mum never takes a plane.

302
00:18:55,010 --> 00:18:57,100
I wanted to take the high-speed rail with her.

303
00:18:57,100 --> 00:18:58,830
But my waist couldn't stand it.

304
00:19:00,470 --> 00:19:01,160
Cheng.

305
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:03,680
This is my dad.

306
00:19:04,820 --> 00:19:05,620
Hello, Uncle.

307
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:07,820
I'll wait for you at Gate 45.

308
00:19:08,110 --> 00:19:09,570
Okay, I'll be right there.

309
00:19:13,290 --> 00:19:14,620
Is this your colleague?

310
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:19,260
All right, I'm still busy.

311
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:21,060
Go back first. Here's the key.

312
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,220
Back to your place?

313
00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:24,350
Are you going to stay in a hotel when your daughter is here?

314
00:19:24,350 --> 00:19:24,740
Okay.

315
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:26,010
I'll call a taxi for you.

316
00:19:26,010 --> 00:19:26,470
No need.

317
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:27,800
I rented a car.

318
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:30,250
This time, I want to stay longer.

319
00:19:30,490 --> 00:19:32,350
It's more convenient to get a car.

320
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:38,200
Then you mustn't let her know

321
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,930
I'm working on ground service.

322
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:40,590
I...

323
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:43,060
I don't want to explain to her.

324
00:19:43,290 --> 00:19:45,270
Don't worry. I understand.

325
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:47,280
When will you get off work?

326
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:47,760
I don't know.

327
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:50,020
I have a lot to do today, so I might be late.

328
00:19:50,060 --> 00:19:51,060
I'll cook for you.

329
00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:52,620
Don't wait for me.

330
00:19:53,040 --> 00:19:53,640
I'll wait for you.

331
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:55,110
I'm not sure. I'll try my best.

332
00:19:55,110 --> 00:19:56,240
Don't wait for me.

333
00:20:12,470 --> 00:20:13,010
Come in.

334
00:20:14,530 --> 00:20:15,130
Mr. Jiang.

335
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:17,810
Cheng.

336
00:20:18,470 --> 00:20:19,070
Come here.

337
00:20:22,270 --> 00:20:22,870
What is it?

338
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:24,850
Well,

339
00:20:24,970 --> 00:20:26,230
I just wanted to ask you

340
00:20:27,040 --> 00:20:29,440
when I can return to the Flight Department.

341
00:20:31,970 --> 00:20:33,950
Are you tired of ground service?

342
00:20:35,470 --> 00:20:38,150
After all, my job is to be a pilot.

343
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:41,010
But

344
00:20:42,360 --> 00:20:44,360
Mr. Gu is your personal instructor.

345
00:20:45,110 --> 00:20:46,590
If anything happens,

346
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,520
shouldn't you go to him first?

347
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:48,950
Right?

348
00:20:50,250 --> 00:20:51,910
He just wants to embarrass me.

349
00:20:52,060 --> 00:20:53,590
Why would he embarrass you?

350
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,140
You're thinking too much.

351
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:56,700
Mr. Gu is not like that.

352
00:20:57,780 --> 00:20:59,780
Approach him and let him know first.

353
00:21:05,090 --> 00:21:05,730
OK?

354
00:21:06,760 --> 00:21:07,480
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

355
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:08,280
You’re welcome.

356
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:09,940
Come to me if he doesn't agree.

357
00:21:10,580 --> 00:21:11,500
I’m leaving.

358
00:21:32,030 --> 00:21:34,150
Pilots must obey the rules pertaining to food and drinks

359
00:21:34,150 --> 00:21:36,350
and not bring food into the flight deck.

360
00:21:36,370 --> 00:21:37,340
During the outstation period,

361
00:21:37,340 --> 00:21:39,550
pilots are not allowed to participate in any high-risk sports.

362
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:41,720
The metal airline badge is to be replaced with soft material.

363
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:42,780
In the flight deck,

364
00:21:42,970 --> 00:21:43,910
the sharp corners of the metal

365
00:21:43,910 --> 00:21:45,570
can cause accidental injury.

366
00:21:47,210 --> 00:21:49,410
There are 128 new regulations in total.

367
00:21:50,410 --> 00:21:51,410
Brother Nanting,

368
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:53,000
you're so thoughtful.

369
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:55,030
You have nipped all the risk factors

370
00:21:55,030 --> 00:21:56,330
in the bud.

371
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:59,260
That's not enough.

372
00:22:00,390 --> 00:22:01,690
I am planning to develop

373
00:22:01,690 --> 00:22:03,200
a safety management system

374
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:04,220
that can cover all aspects

375
00:22:04,220 --> 00:22:05,620
without any blind spots.

376
00:22:05,800 --> 00:22:06,370
I hope

377
00:22:06,890 --> 00:22:09,090
we can achieve the highest safety goal.

378
00:22:11,150 --> 00:22:12,280
What can I do for you?

379
00:22:14,460 --> 00:22:16,320
If you're not afraid of hard work,

380
00:22:16,710 --> 00:22:18,160
you can work on it together with me.

381
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,090
You have no idea.

382
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:21,040
I love bitter gourd with black coffee.

383
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:22,720
And I use a bowl of Chinese medicine as mouthwash.

384
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,030
With such tolerance, I'm a prime candidate

385
00:22:24,030 --> 00:22:25,560
to be an assistant.

386
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:26,450
Fine.

387
00:22:27,670 --> 00:22:30,000
I'll officially hire you as an assistant.

388
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:33,920
Regarding the extra salary, I'll propose it to the company.

389
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,580
Will there be an extra salary?

390
00:22:36,120 --> 00:22:37,750
I just want to learn from you.

391
00:22:49,110 --> 00:22:50,110
Brother Nanting.

392
00:22:52,340 --> 00:22:53,340
When can Xiao

393
00:22:54,220 --> 00:22:56,820
be transferred back to the Flight Department?

394
00:22:58,320 --> 00:22:59,010
Well,

395
00:22:59,950 --> 00:23:01,550
the company will arrange it.

396
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,070
Send those documents

397
00:23:04,070 --> 00:23:06,400
to the Operation Management Department.

398
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:07,770
Okay.

399
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:43,520
How was it?

400
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:47,140
You still need to wait.

401
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:49,870
Xiao, don't worry.

402
00:23:50,410 --> 00:23:51,070
Later,

403
00:23:51,350 --> 00:23:53,410
I'll persuade Brother Nanting more.

404
00:24:24,270 --> 00:24:25,280
Xiaoxiao, you're back.

405
00:24:25,280 --> 00:24:25,610
Dad.

406
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:27,660
Let's eat.

407
00:24:37,710 --> 00:24:39,840
Are you working in ground service now?

408
00:24:39,910 --> 00:24:40,860
It's indeed

409
00:24:41,210 --> 00:24:42,890
a surprising thing.

410
00:24:44,630 --> 00:24:45,960
Who let you into my room?

411
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,210
I'm your mother.

412
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,020
Am I not even allowed

413
00:24:49,020 --> 00:24:50,900
to enter your room?

414
00:24:51,240 --> 00:24:51,720
You...

415
00:24:51,930 --> 00:24:53,390
All right, that's enough.

416
00:24:53,690 --> 00:24:55,220
Xiaoxiao has had a long day.

417
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:57,140
Come on, sit down and eat.

418
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,260
Go wash your hands.

419
00:25:14,910 --> 00:25:15,860
Xiaoxiao

420
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:17,850
is having a learning exchange.

421
00:25:18,020 --> 00:25:18,980
If so, as a judge,

422
00:25:19,010 --> 00:25:20,690
why don't you have a learning exchange

423
00:25:20,690 --> 00:25:22,020
with the prison guards?

424
00:25:22,950 --> 00:25:23,690
Xiaoyun,

425
00:25:23,990 --> 00:25:25,850
Xiaoxiao is already an adult now.

426
00:25:25,880 --> 00:25:27,080
If there's anything,

427
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:29,530
she can take care of it herself.

428
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:31,000
Let her take care of it?

429
00:25:32,300 --> 00:25:33,500
That only resulted in

430
00:25:33,570 --> 00:25:35,720
her transferring to another school in secret.

431
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:36,440
Listen.

432
00:25:36,600 --> 00:25:37,650
If you hadn't

433
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:39,440
indulged and supported her,

434
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:40,210
would things

435
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:41,620
have ended up like this?

436
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:44,410
Cheng Xiao,

437
00:25:45,120 --> 00:25:46,270
listen to me.

438
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:49,080
Go back with me and prepare for the bar examination.

439
00:25:49,080 --> 00:25:49,530
No.

440
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:51,920
Don't even think about it. I won't resign.

441
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:53,040
Besides, I'm staying in Luzhou.

442
00:25:53,040 --> 00:25:54,160
I'm not going anywhere.

443
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,390
Don't try to control me.

444
00:25:55,390 --> 00:25:57,240
I won't let you control me anymore.

445
00:25:57,240 --> 00:25:57,670
Also,

446
00:25:57,880 --> 00:26:00,080
don't enter my room without my permission.

447
00:26:00,080 --> 00:26:01,000
Cheng Xiao, listen.

448
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:02,750
I'm doing this for your own good.

449
00:26:02,750 --> 00:26:04,550
I'm fine. I don't need your help.

450
00:26:05,120 --> 00:26:05,920
Why do you always

451
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:07,760
oppose me?

452
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:08,830
How old are you?

453
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:10,600
Shouldn't you be more mature?

454
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:12,130
You know I'm a grown-up now.

455
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:14,060
It's none of your business. I don't need your control.

456
00:26:14,060 --> 00:26:15,340
I have my own plans.

457
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:22,560
Xiaoxiao, stop it.

458
00:26:22,670 --> 00:26:24,200
I'll get you some medicine.

459
00:26:43,040 --> 00:26:44,100
Take the medicine.

460
00:26:47,410 --> 00:26:48,140
You guys eat.

461
00:26:48,560 --> 00:26:49,300
I'll skip it.

462
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:00,330
Here.

463
00:27:00,750 --> 00:27:01,880
Take your medicine.

464
00:27:31,320 --> 00:27:35,180
[Gu Nanting]

465
00:27:52,130 --> 00:27:52,730
Xiaoxiao.

466
00:27:55,410 --> 00:27:55,800
Dad.

467
00:28:06,780 --> 00:28:07,640
Are you hungry?

468
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:08,920
No.

469
00:28:23,420 --> 00:28:24,750
Your mum has gone to bed.

470
00:28:30,280 --> 00:28:32,850
Has she been taking antihypertensive medicine?

471
00:28:32,850 --> 00:28:33,660
Why do I feel

472
00:28:34,300 --> 00:28:35,500
nothing has changed?

473
00:28:36,120 --> 00:28:38,050
Do we need to take her to the doctor?

474
00:28:39,230 --> 00:28:39,690
No need.

475
00:28:41,150 --> 00:28:42,210
Her blood pressure

476
00:28:42,960 --> 00:28:44,320
is still unstable.

477
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:46,060
It's nothing serious.

478
00:28:52,490 --> 00:28:53,120
Xiaoxiao,

479
00:28:54,250 --> 00:28:55,300
tell me the truth.

480
00:28:56,710 --> 00:28:59,170
Why did you transfer to become ground staff?

481
00:29:07,030 --> 00:29:07,440
Dad.

482
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:09,660
Actually,

483
00:29:11,100 --> 00:29:12,960
there's indeed some fluctuation

484
00:29:13,670 --> 00:29:14,650
in my work.

485
00:29:15,790 --> 00:29:18,960
I was transferred from the Freight Department to the Passenger Flight Department at first.

486
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:19,510
Later,

487
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:22,920
I was transferred to the Ground Handling Department

488
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:25,170
because I made some mistakes in my work.

489
00:29:25,910 --> 00:29:28,310
But I will return to the Flight Department.

490
00:29:33,660 --> 00:29:34,260
Xiaoxiao,

491
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,000
I believe

492
00:29:36,470 --> 00:29:37,800
you will get through it.

493
00:29:41,080 --> 00:29:41,620
But

494
00:29:42,390 --> 00:29:44,320
if you encounter any difficulties,

495
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:45,340
you must tell me.

496
00:29:47,120 --> 00:29:48,250
Don't worry, Cheng.

497
00:29:48,330 --> 00:29:49,660
Your daughter is tough.

498
00:29:50,880 --> 00:29:52,250
Alright. Just go.

499
00:30:56,500 --> 00:31:00,520
[Online College Application for High School Students, Shandong Province, 2010]

500
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:02,560
Why did you change my college application

501
00:31:02,560 --> 00:31:03,890
without my permission?

502
00:31:04,080 --> 00:31:06,770
Going to law school is your best choice.

503
00:31:07,310 --> 00:31:08,760
You're a lawyer.

504
00:31:08,760 --> 00:31:10,820
But now you're invading my personal rights.

505
00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:12,310
Without me,

506
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:14,640
how did you get the awards on the wall?

507
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:16,480
Math Olympiad, violin, essays.

508
00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:17,840
Could you have such good grades?

509
00:31:17,840 --> 00:31:19,760
These are all things that you like.

510
00:31:19,760 --> 00:31:21,880
What you like is not what I like.

511
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:23,080
You forced me to do it.

512
00:31:23,250 --> 00:31:24,270
I don't like it.

513
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:38,560
Dad.

514
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,480
Why are you here?

515
00:31:43,810 --> 00:31:44,820
I'm here

516
00:31:45,060 --> 00:31:46,590
behind your mother's back.

517
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:48,860
Look.

518
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:50,210
What is this?

519
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:57,820
[Acceptance Letter to Beijing University of Aeronautics and Astronautics]

520
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,900
I can transfer to another school.

521
00:32:03,600 --> 00:32:04,200
Xiaoxiao,

522
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:05,140
I know

523
00:32:05,460 --> 00:32:07,060
you've always liked flying.

524
00:32:07,820 --> 00:32:10,220
Now that you're really studying this major,

525
00:32:10,220 --> 00:32:11,020
I hope you will

526
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:12,850
hang in there.

527
00:32:13,700 --> 00:32:15,100
I'll always support you.

528
00:32:18,590 --> 00:32:20,570
Cheng, you're so good to me.

529
00:32:21,530 --> 00:32:22,770
I love you.

530
00:32:24,430 --> 00:32:25,160
Don’t worry.

531
00:32:25,510 --> 00:32:27,160
I will become a captain in the future.

532
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,290
I won't let you down.

533
00:33:23,320 --> 00:33:24,490
Hello, are you going to Shenzhen?

534
00:33:24,490 --> 00:33:25,070
Yes.

535
00:33:25,930 --> 00:33:27,240
Okay, you may get in the car.

536
00:33:27,240 --> 00:33:27,640
Hello.

537
00:33:27,710 --> 00:33:28,170
Hello.

538
00:33:29,640 --> 00:33:30,000
Let me do it.

539
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:30,400
Okay, thank you.

540
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:30,960
Get in the car first.

541
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:31,760
OK. Thank you.

542
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:33,820
Cheng Xiao.

543
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:38,080
Mr. Ni.

544
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:39,880
Why are you...

545
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:44,850
I'm training at the Ground Handling Department.

546
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:47,760
Are you going on a business trip today?

547
00:33:47,760 --> 00:33:48,550
I was going to fly,

548
00:33:48,550 --> 00:33:51,350
but something came up. I changed my flight to this afternoon.

549
00:33:51,350 --> 00:33:52,500
When are we leaving?

550
00:33:53,280 --> 00:33:54,070
Soon.

551
00:33:54,850 --> 00:33:55,420
Go ahead.

552
00:34:00,180 --> 00:34:00,900
Sorry.

553
00:34:01,470 --> 00:34:02,070
It's okay.

554
00:34:05,630 --> 00:34:06,810
Sit tight. Let's go.

555
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:34,420
Yue.

556
00:34:35,250 --> 00:34:36,050
Where are you?

557
00:34:36,560 --> 00:34:37,820
I'm in my boss' office.

558
00:34:38,090 --> 00:34:39,719
I was tidying up the data until late at night,

559
00:34:39,719 --> 00:34:40,580
so I fell asleep

560
00:34:40,710 --> 00:34:41,909
and missed your call.

561
00:34:42,179 --> 00:34:42,840
Which boss?

562
00:34:43,570 --> 00:34:44,300
Is it a woman?

563
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:45,270
No, no.

564
00:34:45,389 --> 00:34:47,130
It's a man. It's definitely a man.

565
00:34:47,130 --> 00:34:49,179
Why didn't you sleep in Cai's office

566
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:52,440
when you worked in the Freight Department?

567
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:56,620
Resign from that assistant position immediately.

568
00:34:57,730 --> 00:34:59,290
Can we stop joking, Yue?

569
00:34:59,520 --> 00:35:00,520
If you don't quit,

570
00:35:00,600 --> 00:35:01,860
let's not be together.

571
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:03,450
Don't be unreasonable.

572
00:35:19,700 --> 00:35:20,130
Hello.

573
00:35:21,020 --> 00:35:21,940
You are...

574
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:25,360
Mr. Ni from the Maintenance Department.

575
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,830
I'm here to wait for Nanting to come to work.

576
00:35:26,830 --> 00:35:28,170
When Brother Nanting doesn't fly,

577
00:35:28,170 --> 00:35:29,330
he comes to the office at 9 am.

578
00:35:29,330 --> 00:35:30,280
Not even a second off.

579
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,630
He's just a walking clock.

580
00:35:31,630 --> 00:35:32,560
Why are you here?

