It was Mr. Jiang’s decision.

600
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:31,120
I also think that

601
00:36:31,240 --> 00:36:32,800
no matter what mistake Cheng Xiao made,

602
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:35,110
she shouldn't be transferred to ground service.

603
00:36:35,110 --> 00:36:35,730
I plan to

604
00:36:36,080 --> 00:36:37,280
talk to Mr. Xu

605
00:36:37,650 --> 00:36:38,580
once he returns.

606
00:36:39,150 --> 00:36:40,700
