608
00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:44,010
We will just talk about the facts.

609
00:36:44,310 --> 00:36:46,040
It's indeed your personality.

610
00:36:49,500 --> 00:36:50,300
Actually,

611
00:36:51,030 --> 00:36:52,390
