612
00:37:09,020 --> 00:37:10,260
What's the reason for the delay?

613
00:37:10,260 --> 00:37:11,010
Shouldn't we

614
00:37:11,030 --> 00:37:12,540
explain it to the passengers?

615
00:37:12,540 --> 00:37:13,570
We haven't received

616
00:37:13,570 --> 00:37:15,030
any specific reasons yet.

617
00:37:22,700 --> 00:37:24,560
There is a thunderstorm on the flight path.

618
00:37:24,560 --> 00:37:26,200
The nearest route to Guangzhou

619
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:28,130
is also covered by thunderstorms.

620
00:37:29,100 --> 00:37:31,300
The airport needs to be adjusted, and the route needs to be controlled.

621
00:37:31,300 --> 00:37:33,390
Moreover, there's a go-around difference.

622
00:37:33,390 --> 00:37:35,320
We don't know how long it will take.

623
00:37:36,520 --> 00:37:38,050
God is just like humans.

624
00:37:38,270 --> 00:37:39,870
Sometimes he's in a bad mood.

625
00:37:41,240 --> 00:37:41,770
Zhengyu.

626
00:37:41,790 --> 00:37:42,720
The food is here.

627
00:37:42,890 --> 00:37:44,000
Deliver them the food first.

628
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:44,330
Okay.

629
00:37:47,280 --> 00:37:48,410
Hello, passengers.

630
00:37:48,520 --> 00:37:49,840
Attention all passengers

631
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:51,860
herading to Guangzhou

632
00:37:51,890 --> 00:37:53,570
aboard flight XD8311 with Luzhou airlines.

633
00:37:53,570 --> 00:37:55,690
We will now distribute meals for you.

634
00:37:55,720 --> 00:37:57,400
Please have your boarding pass ready

635
00:37:57,400 --> 00:37:58,950
and wait patiently in your seats.

636
00:37:58,950 --> 00:38:01,810
Thank you for your understanding and cooperation.

637
00:38:03,870 --> 00:38:04,870
Here's your meal.

638
00:38:05,230 --> 00:38:06,560
Sorry to keep you waiting.

639
00:38:06,560 --> 00:38:07,240
The meal is ready.

640
00:38:07,240 --> 00:38:08,770
Are we not allowed to leave?

641
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:10,400
Yeah, how long is it going to take?

642
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:11,620
How long will it take?

643
00:38:12,080 --> 00:38:12,750
Sorry.

644
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:14,980
We’re waiting for the captain’s order.

645
00:38:14,980 --> 00:38:16,460
When can we take off?

646
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:18,000
We, as the ground staff, are also unclear

647
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:19,440
about the situation.

648
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:20,520
So we can't give

649
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:21,200
the exact time.

650
00:38:21,200 --> 00:38:21,680
Please understand that.

651
00:38:21,680 --> 00:38:22,680
Why didn't you report

652
00:38:22,680 --> 00:38:23,680
the delayed flight?

653
00:38:23,680 --> 00:38:24,340
Yeah.

654
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:26,490
You have to tell us the reason.

655
00:38:26,510 --> 00:38:27,390
Otherwise, we wouldn't know

656
00:38:27,390 --> 00:38:28,360
what's going on, right?

657
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:31,320
Yes, give us a reason. Yes.

658
00:38:32,030 --> 00:38:33,630
It's because of the weather.

659
00:38:34,360 --> 00:38:35,210
Weather?

660
00:38:35,740 --> 00:38:37,660
The weather is so nice outside.

661
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:39,300
I checked the weather in Guangzhou.

662
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:41,320
There's no wind or rain, and no fog also.

663
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:42,320
Here's the thing.

664
00:38:42,340 --> 00:38:44,440
There are many different situations that could happen with the weather.

665
00:38:44,440 --> 00:38:47,170
Apart from an inability to takeoff at the departure airport

666
00:38:47,170 --> 00:38:49,370
and to land at the destination airport,

667
00:38:49,370 --> 00:38:50,480
there is another situation.

668
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:51,960
It is that the weather on the flight path

669
00:38:51,960 --> 00:38:53,880
is not suitable for flying.

670
00:38:54,040 --> 00:38:55,200
We just checked.

671
00:38:55,300 --> 00:38:56,880
There's a thunderstorm area on the flight path.

672
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:57,920
The sky is so big.

673
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:59,520
Can't you just take a detour?

674
00:38:59,600 --> 00:39:02,000
There are many planes in the sky,

675
00:39:02,020 --> 00:39:03,080
just like on a road.

676
00:39:03,550 --> 00:39:06,160
Besides, due to flight safety and national defense needs,

677
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:08,550
the flight path for commercial flights is limited.

678
00:39:08,550 --> 00:39:11,480
There's very little room for a detour or a go-around.

679
00:39:11,510 --> 00:39:12,110
Alright.

680
00:39:13,180 --> 00:39:14,380
You're wasting time.

681
00:39:34,750 --> 00:39:35,480
You go first.

682
00:39:53,660 --> 00:39:54,590
How is your work?

683
00:39:56,060 --> 00:39:59,190
Are you still in charge of me even when I'm a ground staff?

684
00:39:59,390 --> 00:40:02,650
After all, you are still a member of our Flight Department.

685
00:40:03,700 --> 00:40:04,300
So,

686
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:06,720
when can I return to the Flight Department?

687
00:40:18,640 --> 00:40:19,210
Hello.

688
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:21,110
Okay.

689
00:40:22,370 --> 00:40:23,830
Mechanical malfunction.

690
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:27,990
Dear passengers,

691
00:40:27,990 --> 00:40:29,240
I'm sorry to inform you

692
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:32,310
that flight XD831 to Guangzhou

693
00:40:32,340 --> 00:40:33,440
has had a mechanical malfunction.

694
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:35,220
The repair cannot be done in a short period.

695
00:40:35,220 --> 00:40:37,190
Please wait patiently for further notice.

696
00:40:37,190 --> 00:40:37,790
Thank you.

697
00:40:38,910 --> 00:40:40,370
Mechanical malfunction.

698
00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:41,740
Didn't you say it's because of the weather?

699
00:40:41,740 --> 00:40:42,750
What's going on?

700
00:40:45,510 --> 00:40:47,790
We just received a notice that it's a mechanical malfunction.

701
00:40:47,790 --> 00:40:49,650
But there was indeed a thunderstorm on the flight path.

702
00:40:49,650 --> 00:40:50,650
Cut the crap.

703
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:52,170
You need to compensate if it's a mechanical malfunction.

704
00:40:52,170 --> 00:40:53,450
But you don't need to if it's because of the weather.

705
00:40:53,450 --> 00:40:54,760
Are you trying to deny our compensation?

706
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:56,860
If it's delayed by a mechanical malfunction,

707
00:40:56,860 --> 00:40:58,670
you must compensate us immediately.

708
00:40:58,670 --> 00:40:59,870
Sir, we have a rule.

709
00:40:59,890 --> 00:41:01,520
Only when it's delayed for more than four hours,

710
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:02,960
can we arrange for accommodation

711
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:03,840
or make compensation.

712
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:05,080
Please wait patiently.

713
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:06,440
I don't have that patience.

714
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:07,880
How long do we have to wait?

715
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:08,600
Sorry, sir.

716
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,000
We can't be sure.

717
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:10,480
It depends on

718
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:12,160
what has caused the mechanical malfunction.

719
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:12,840
Here's the thing.

720
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:14,440
If it's a flight control computer,

721
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:16,120
it will take two hours to repair it.

722
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:17,200
If it's a severe malfunction,

723
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:18,600
such as an engine,

724
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:19,640
it may take three hours

725
00:41:19,640 --> 00:41:20,560
because we need to change the plane.

726
00:41:20,560 --> 00:41:21,520
Nonsense.

727
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:22,320
I can't wait anymore.

728
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:23,240
Sir, calm down.

729
00:41:23,270 --> 00:41:24,330
Please calm down.

730
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:26,030
Sir.

731
00:41:26,950 --> 00:41:27,480
Cheng.

732
00:41:27,950 --> 00:41:28,350
I...

733
00:41:29,430 --> 00:41:29,850
I...

734
00:41:37,060 --> 00:41:38,170
What are you doing?

735
00:41:38,230 --> 00:41:39,360
Do you want to hit me?

736
00:41:52,250 --> 00:41:53,800
Someone is making trouble at Gate 79.

737
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:54,860
What are you doing?

738
00:41:56,330 --> 00:41:57,260
Let go!

739
00:41:59,680 --> 00:42:00,180
Let go!

740
00:42:00,340 --> 00:42:01,950
There are surveillance cameras at all the boarding gates.

741
00:42:01,950 --> 00:42:03,680
I recorded everything you did.

742
00:42:07,920 --> 00:42:08,780
What happened?

743
00:42:08,830 --> 00:42:09,520
This man was making a scene

744
00:42:09,520 --> 00:42:11,320
and splashed water on our staff.

745
00:42:13,180 --> 00:42:14,240
Hello, passenger.

746
00:42:14,690 --> 00:42:16,320
I'm a police officer at the Luzhou Airport.

747
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:17,200
What you did just now

748
00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:18,480
