749
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:19,540
Please cooperate with our investigation

750
00:42:19,540 --> 00:42:20,800
at the police station.

751
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:23,660
Please come with us

752
00:42:23,910 --> 00:42:25,970
to help us understand the situation.

753
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:28,370
Let's go.

